00:42:58,840 --> 00:43:01,320
[SPEAKER_00] ugušiti, koliko god ga se pokušavalo

1133
00:43:01,320 --> 00:43:03,280
[SPEAKER_00] nivelirati, pretvoriti sve

1134
00:43:03,280 --> 00:43:05,320
[SPEAKER_00] u nekakav opći, evropski,

1135
00:43:05,320 --> 00:43:07,659
[SPEAKER_00] zajednički sentiment i osjećaj,

1136
00:43:07,739 --> 00:43:09,199
[SPEAKER_00] to neće ići, dakle, to jednostavno

1137
00:43:09,199 --> 00:43:10,360
[SPEAKER_00] ne funkcionira na taj način.

1138
00:43:10,360 --> 00:43:11,500
[SPEAKER_01] Sad, pavljeste, mi doslovno smo

1139
00:43:11,500 --> 00:43:12,559
[SPEAKER_01] isključeni iz pregovora,

1140
00:43:12,559 --> 00:43:13,840
[SPEAKER_01] ratuje se na evropskom tlu.

1141
00:43:13,840 --> 00:43:16,780
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, to je onako malo ponižavajuće,

1142
00:43:16,780 --> 00:43:17,019
[SPEAKER_01] je li da?

1143
00:43:17,019 --> 00:43:19,340
[SPEAKER_00] Malo je ponižavajuće, ali mi sami smo

1144
00:43:19,340 --> 00:43:21,400
[SPEAKER_00] krivi što smo se doveli

1145
00:43:21,400 --> 00:43:22,300
[SPEAKER_00] u takvu situaciju.

1146
00:43:22,300 --> 00:43:22,579
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

1147
00:43:22,579 --> 00:43:25,420
[SPEAKER_01] Gospodine, je ono će teško je podviđati.

1148
00:43:25,420 --> 00:43:27,239
[SPEAKER_01] Sve mislite subijno Ukrajine,

1149
00:43:27,239 --> 00:43:28,960
[SPEAKER_01] sad moramo je se da takrat, mislim.

1150
00:43:28,960 --> 00:43:30,860
[SPEAKER_00] Moji su simpatije na ukrajinskoj strani,

1151
00:43:30,980 --> 00:43:32,820
[SPEAKER_00] O tome nema apsolutno nikakve dvojbe.

1152
00:43:32,820 --> 00:43:34,880
[SPEAKER_00] Ja bi želio da Ukrajina iziđe

1153
00:43:34,880 --> 00:43:37,960
[SPEAKER_00] iz rata, dakle, teritorijalno neokrnjena

1154
00:43:37,960 --> 00:43:39,219
[SPEAKER_00] i politički stažna.

1155
00:43:39,219 --> 00:43:41,900
[SPEAKER_00] Bojim se da se to tako neće dogoditi,

1156
00:43:41,900 --> 00:43:45,920
[SPEAKER_00] ali uvijek treba biti svjesan

1157
00:43:45,920 --> 00:43:47,460
[SPEAKER_00] da je ono što se govori

1158
00:43:47,460 --> 00:43:48,880
[SPEAKER_00] kao nekakva opća formula

1159
00:43:48,880 --> 00:43:50,039
[SPEAKER_00] da je nepravedan mir

1160
00:43:50,039 --> 00:43:53,219
[SPEAKER_00] je zametak novoga sukoba,

1161
00:43:53,219 --> 00:43:53,860
[SPEAKER_00] novoga rata.

1162
00:43:53,860 --> 00:43:55,480
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, nije bilo slučajno

1163
00:43:55,480 --> 00:43:57,139
[SPEAKER_00] kad su dalekovidni ljudi

1164
00:43:57,139 --> 00:43:59,099
[SPEAKER_00] čuši kako glasi

1165
00:43:59,099 --> 00:44:00,199
[SPEAKER_00] versajski sporazum.

1166
00:44:00,199 --> 00:44:01,239
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ja sad citiram

1167
00:44:01,239 --> 00:44:03,760
[SPEAKER_00] francuskog maršala,

1168
00:44:03,760 --> 00:44:05,179
[SPEAKER_00] jednoga, dakle, koji je na vijest

1169
00:44:05,179 --> 00:44:06,860
[SPEAKER_00] o sklapanju versajskog sporazuma,

1170
00:44:06,860 --> 00:44:10,079
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, koji je Njemačku desetkovao

1171
00:44:10,079 --> 00:44:11,599
[SPEAKER_00] nakon prvog svjetskog rata,

1172
00:44:11,599 --> 00:44:12,840
[SPEAKER_00] kazao ovo nije mir,

1173
00:44:12,840 --> 00:44:15,159
[SPEAKER_00] nego je primjer je na 20 godina.

1174
00:44:15,159 --> 00:44:16,880
[SPEAKER_00] I pokazalo se savršeno, precizno,

1175
00:44:16,880 --> 00:44:18,199
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, jer ste jednostavno

1176
00:44:18,199 --> 00:44:19,880
[SPEAKER_00] povrijedili, ponizili jedan narod

1177
00:44:19,880 --> 00:44:23,380
[SPEAKER_00] u kojem će tinjati nezadovojstvo

1178
00:44:23,380 --> 00:44:24,400
[SPEAKER_00] dok to nezadovojstvo

1179
00:44:24,400 --> 00:44:25,420
[SPEAKER_00] jednom ne rumpira,

1180
00:44:25,420 --> 00:44:27,380
[SPEAKER_00] dok jednom, dakle, ne iziđe na svjetla dana

1181
00:44:27,380 --> 00:44:29,760
[SPEAKER_00] i ne bih želio, dakle, da

1182
00:44:29,760 --> 00:44:32,420
[SPEAKER_00] možda mi to nećemo doživjeti,

1183
00:44:32,420 --> 00:44:33,579
[SPEAKER_00] ali ne bih želio da to dožive

1184
00:44:33,579 --> 00:44:34,679
[SPEAKER_00] moja djeca, moji unuci,

1185
00:44:34,679 --> 00:44:35,320
[SPEAKER_00] da dožive

1186
00:44:35,320 --> 00:44:39,500
[SPEAKER_00] posljedice onoga što se možda

1187
00:44:39,500 --> 00:44:40,840
[SPEAKER_00] dogodi danas.

1188
00:44:40,840 --> 00:44:42,599
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim, mi smo premali,

1189
00:44:42,599 --> 00:44:43,719
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, mi kao Hrvati,

1190
00:44:43,719 --> 00:44:45,219
[SPEAKER_00] Hrvatski narod i Hrvatska država,

1191
00:44:45,219 --> 00:44:47,059
[SPEAKER_00] mi smo premali da bi smo u tome mogli

1192
00:44:47,059 --> 00:44:48,760
[SPEAKER_00] presudno uđati.

1193
00:44:48,840 --> 00:44:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bili smo malo glasni,

1194
00:44:50,000 --> 00:44:52,360
[SPEAKER_01] ali evo sad primijetim i premijer i predsjednik Šut.

1195
00:44:52,360 --> 00:44:55,940
[SPEAKER_01] Da, jer su, dakle, bili,

1196
00:44:55,940 --> 00:44:58,380
[SPEAKER_00] pogotovo predsjednik vlade je bio zagrizao,

1197
00:44:58,380 --> 00:45:01,380
[SPEAKER_00] zaloga je veći od onoga koji može progutati,

1198
00:45:01,380 --> 00:45:04,139
[SPEAKER_00] pa je sad shvatio, dakle, da se mora curikati.

1199
00:45:04,139 --> 00:45:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer ovo je, ajmo reć,

1200
00:45:06,000 --> 00:45:07,679
[SPEAKER_01] ispravi teme slobodno,

1201
00:45:07,920 --> 00:45:10,860
[SPEAKER_01] vrlo direktna, ali i ružna poruka

1202
00:45:10,860 --> 00:45:11,739
[SPEAKER_01] jedne Amerike,

1203
00:45:11,739 --> 00:45:14,119
[SPEAKER_01] Ukrajincima i Savjeznicima.

1204
00:45:14,119 --> 00:45:16,440
[SPEAKER_01] Ono, pay per view,

1205
00:45:16,440 --> 00:45:17,800
[SPEAKER_01] plati pa te brani.

1206
00:45:17,800 --> 00:45:18,300
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je.

1207
00:45:18,300 --> 00:45:20,380
[SPEAKER_01] Nije da mi nismo znali da je

1208
00:45:20,380 --> 00:45:22,739
[SPEAKER_01] i Bajdenova administracija imala tu interesa,

1209
00:45:22,739 --> 00:45:23,719
[SPEAKER_01] svi uvijek imaju interesa,

1210
00:45:23,719 --> 00:45:25,400
[SPEAKER_01] ali ovo je bilo ono direktno,

1211
00:45:25,400 --> 00:45:26,900
[SPEAKER_01] ko bok su šakom u glavu.

1212
00:45:26,900 --> 00:45:28,340
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo je bilo potpuno otvoreno

1213
00:45:28,340 --> 00:45:29,219
[SPEAKER_00] i nedvosmisleno.

1214
00:45:29,219 --> 00:45:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kako bi sad mi se trebali kao evropljeni ponašati?

1215
00:45:32,000 --> 00:45:34,920
[SPEAKER_00] Nismo navikuli na taj način ophođenja,

1216
00:45:34,920 --> 00:45:36,380
[SPEAKER_00] ali očito ćemo se morati navikavati,

1217
00:45:36,460 --> 00:45:37,480
[SPEAKER_00] ono što ste u jednom trenutku

1218
00:45:37,480 --> 00:45:38,940
[SPEAKER_00] u današnjem našem razgovoru kazali,

1219
00:45:38,940 --> 00:45:42,760
[SPEAKER_00] prošlo vrijeme diplomacije u rukavicama.

1220
00:45:42,760 --> 00:45:45,880
[SPEAKER_00] Jasno, dakle, to vrijeme je očito prošlo.

1221
00:45:45,880 --> 00:45:46,820
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, vraćamo se,

1222
00:45:46,820 --> 00:45:50,440
[SPEAKER_00] jer bilo je prije 60-70 godina,

1223
00:45:50,440 --> 00:45:51,699
[SPEAKER_00] slično tako vrijeme, dakle,

1224
00:45:51,699 --> 00:45:53,119
[SPEAKER_00] u kojem su postojali diktati

1225
00:45:53,119 --> 00:45:54,280
[SPEAKER_00] i u kojem se niste mogli

1226
00:45:54,280 --> 00:45:56,780
[SPEAKER_00] pozvati ni na međunarodno pravo,

1227
00:45:56,780 --> 00:45:58,659
[SPEAKER_00] ni na diplomatsko ophođenje,

1228
00:45:58,659 --> 00:45:59,960
[SPEAKER_00] nego je vrijedila gola sila.

1229
00:45:59,960 --> 00:46:02,760
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, govorimo o vremenu konfrontacije

1230
00:46:02,760 --> 00:46:04,579
[SPEAKER_00] koja je dovela do drugog svjetskog rata.

1231
00:46:04,579 --> 00:46:04,940
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle,

1232
00:46:05,000 --> 00:46:08,579
[SPEAKER_00] ponovno ulazimo u to razdoblje,

1233
00:46:08,579 --> 00:46:10,800
[SPEAKER_00] nadajmo se da ono neće biti tako traumatično,

1234
00:46:10,800 --> 00:46:13,219
[SPEAKER_00] da neće biti tako krvavo kao što je bilo ono.

1235
00:46:13,219 --> 00:46:15,260
[SPEAKER_01] Da, kak bi rekli bakice na placu,

1236
00:46:15,260 --> 00:46:16,639
[SPEAKER_01] čime ću platiti Americi,

1237
00:46:16,639 --> 00:46:17,280
[SPEAKER_01] sve smo dali.

1238
00:46:17,280 --> 00:46:17,860
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da.

1239
00:46:17,860 --> 00:46:18,760
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, tako,

1240
00:46:18,760 --> 00:46:20,519
[SPEAKER_01] da, šerif, da, dobro,

1241
00:46:20,519 --> 00:46:21,800
[SPEAKER_01] evo je njegov rekao, šerif je,

1242
00:46:21,800 --> 00:46:24,059
[SPEAKER_01] vidit ćemo sad šta će biti.

1243
00:46:24,440 --> 00:46:26,920
[SPEAKER_01] Kako biste mogli na našu regiju odrasiti?

1244
00:46:26,920 --> 00:46:29,940
[SPEAKER_01] Sad, kad govorite regiju,

1245
00:46:29,940 --> 00:46:32,099
[SPEAKER_00] ne govorite o Karlovačkoj regiji.

1246
00:46:32,099 --> 00:46:33,579
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, ne, ne, nego u Hrvatskoj.

1247
00:46:33,579 --> 00:46:35,500
[SPEAKER_01] Odnosno, području Bivše Jugoslavije.

1248
00:46:35,500 --> 00:46:38,800
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ja bi prvo izbjegao taj termin uopći,

1249
00:46:38,800 --> 00:46:42,059
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, jer ne vidim nikakva razloga da se mi uspoređujemo

1250
00:46:42,059 --> 00:46:43,320
[SPEAKER_00] sa, ovaj,

1251
00:46:43,320 --> 00:46:45,440
[SPEAKER_00] ono je područjeno koje je pripadalo

1252
00:46:45,440 --> 00:46:46,599
[SPEAKER_00] Bivše Jugoslavije.

1253
00:46:46,599 --> 00:46:48,360
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ne treba ni na koji način

1254
00:46:48,360 --> 00:46:51,079
[SPEAKER_00] održavati predođbu o tome

1255
00:46:51,079 --> 00:46:52,320
[SPEAKER_00] da je to nekakav jedinstveni,

1256
00:46:52,320 --> 00:46:54,699
[SPEAKER_00] geopolitički, kulturni, civilizacijski prostor.

1257
00:46:54,699 --> 00:46:56,500
[SPEAKER_00] To su države koje su nastale

1258
00:46:56,500 --> 00:46:59,139
[SPEAKER_00] i koje će, po svemu sudeći,

1259
00:46:59,139 --> 00:47:00,860
[SPEAKER_00] obstati, dakle, koji će samostalno

1260
00:47:00,860 --> 00:47:01,800
[SPEAKER_00] kreirati svoju sudbinu.

1261
00:47:01,800 --> 00:47:03,840
[SPEAKER_00] Zbog toga, kad mi se kaže regija,

1262
00:47:03,840 --> 00:47:05,260
[SPEAKER_00] ja mislim na Zagrebačku regiju,

1263
00:47:05,260 --> 00:47:07,219
[SPEAKER_00] Splitsku, Riječku, Osječku i tako dalje,

1264
00:47:07,219 --> 00:47:08,699
[SPEAKER_00] ništa šire od toga.

1265
00:47:12,059 --> 00:47:14,980
[SPEAKER_00] Ključni naš interes u Bosni i Hercegovine,

1266
00:47:14,980 --> 00:47:16,840
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, jer je tamo glavnina,

1267
00:47:16,840 --> 00:47:19,539
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno dobar dio hrvatskog naroda,

1268
00:47:19,539 --> 00:47:22,360
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, koji je zapravo obespravljen,

1269
00:47:22,360 --> 00:47:26,659
[SPEAKER_00] koji već godinama ili zapravo desetljećima

1270
00:47:26,659 --> 00:47:28,800
[SPEAKER_00] ne uspjeva izabrati,

1271
00:47:28,800 --> 00:47:30,380
[SPEAKER_00] ne dopuštamo se izabrati

1272
