[SPEAKER_00] vlastite legitimne predstavnike

1273
00:47:32,039 --> 00:47:36,059
[SPEAKER_00] i mislim da je naš nacionalni državni interes

1274
00:47:36,059 --> 00:47:37,559
[SPEAKER_00] primarno, dakle, osiguranje

1275
00:47:37,559 --> 00:47:40,699
[SPEAKER_00] položaje jednakopravnosti Hroata

1276
00:47:40,699 --> 00:47:42,159
[SPEAKER_00] u Bosni i Hercegovini,

1277
00:47:42,159 --> 00:47:44,440
[SPEAKER_00] a to je ujedno sredstvo kojim se ta država

1278
00:47:44,440 --> 00:47:46,179
[SPEAKER_00] može održati na okupu,

1279
00:47:46,179 --> 00:47:48,219
[SPEAKER_00] jer onog trenutka, dakle, kad njezini narodi,

1280
00:47:48,219 --> 00:47:50,219
[SPEAKER_00] govorimo o tri konstitutivna naroda,

1281
00:47:50,219 --> 00:47:51,400
[SPEAKER_00] kad oni nisu zadovoljni,

1282
00:47:51,400 --> 00:47:52,400
[SPEAKER_00] kad se oni osjećaju,

1283
00:47:52,400 --> 00:47:53,400
[SPEAKER_00] neki od njih,

1284
00:47:53,400 --> 00:47:55,619
[SPEAKER_00] kad se osjećaju bespravljenim,

1285
00:47:55,619 --> 00:47:58,219
[SPEAKER_00] to je zapravo otvaranje puta

1286
00:47:58,219 --> 00:48:00,760
[SPEAKER_00] u nerede, u kaos

1287
00:48:00,760 --> 00:48:02,940
[SPEAKER_00] i u disoluciju raspad te države.

1288
00:48:02,940 --> 00:48:04,139
[SPEAKER_00] To je nešto što mislim da

1289
00:48:04,139 --> 00:48:06,380
[SPEAKER_00] hrvatskome narodu ne bi odgovarilo,

1290
00:48:06,380 --> 00:48:07,739
[SPEAKER_00] ne bi odgovarilo hrvatskoj državi.

1291
00:48:07,739 --> 00:48:11,219
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim da će Srbija probati skolisito na uštad,

1292
00:48:11,219 --> 00:48:11,639
[SPEAKER_01] recimo,

1293
00:48:11,639 --> 00:48:13,719
[SPEAKER_01] da je Trumpovi administracije

1294
00:48:13,719 --> 00:48:15,179
[SPEAKER_01] po pitanju Republike Srpske,

1295
00:48:15,179 --> 00:48:15,940
[SPEAKER_01] da malo...

1296
00:48:15,940 --> 00:48:17,199
[SPEAKER_01] Ja ne sumnjam da...

1297
00:48:17,199 --> 00:48:17,900
[SPEAKER_01] Sad je vidljio,

1298
00:48:17,900 --> 00:48:18,820
[SPEAKER_01] pardon, da je Vučić,

1299
00:48:18,820 --> 00:48:19,599
[SPEAKER_01] ajmo reći,

1300
00:48:19,599 --> 00:48:20,400
[SPEAKER_01] brislanski igrač.

1301
00:48:20,400 --> 00:48:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ne sumnjam u to,

1302
00:48:22,000 --> 00:48:24,219
[SPEAKER_00] da u Srbiji postoji takav interes

1303
00:48:24,219 --> 00:48:25,860
[SPEAKER_00] i da je to zapravo dubinska želja

1304
00:48:25,860 --> 00:48:28,179
[SPEAKER_00] velikog dijela Srpske ili Srbijanske.

1305
00:48:28,179 --> 00:48:29,599
[SPEAKER_00] Srpske, dakle, kad govorim,

1306
00:48:29,599 --> 00:48:30,920
[SPEAKER_00] ne samo one koji su u Srbiji,

1307
00:48:30,920 --> 00:48:31,739
[SPEAKER_00] nego i uopće,

1308
00:48:31,739 --> 00:48:33,480
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, srpske političke elite

1309
00:48:33,480 --> 00:48:35,219
[SPEAKER_00] i u BiH i u Hrvatskoj.

1310
00:48:35,219 --> 00:48:36,619
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, svi bi oni zapravo htjeli

1311
00:48:36,619 --> 00:48:38,119
[SPEAKER_00] prekrajanje granica,

1312
00:48:38,119 --> 00:48:38,960
[SPEAKER_00] to je ono što je

1313
00:48:38,960 --> 00:48:40,619
[SPEAKER_00] Patriar Srpske pravoslavne crkve

1314
00:48:40,619 --> 00:48:42,780
[SPEAKER_00] podsjetio nas ne tako davno,

1315
00:48:42,780 --> 00:48:44,239
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, da su granice promjenjive

1316
00:48:44,239 --> 00:48:46,599
[SPEAKER_00] i da ne treba odustati od onoga

1317
00:48:46,599 --> 00:48:47,380
[SPEAKER_00] što oni nazivaju

1318
00:48:47,380 --> 00:48:48,559
[SPEAKER_00] zapadnim srpskim krajevima,

1319
00:48:48,559 --> 00:48:49,719
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno srpskim svetom.

1320
00:48:49,719 --> 00:48:50,960
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, neće ti,

1321
00:48:50,960 --> 00:48:52,599
[SPEAKER_00] te ambicije i te težnje

1322
00:48:52,599 --> 00:48:53,320
[SPEAKER_00] neće prestati,

1323
00:48:53,440 --> 00:48:54,500
[SPEAKER_00] međutim, mislim da smo mi

1324
00:48:54,500 --> 00:48:55,340
[SPEAKER_00] dovoljno jake,

1325
00:48:55,340 --> 00:48:56,719
[SPEAKER_00] da je Srbija dovoljno slaba,

1326
00:48:56,719 --> 00:48:58,559
[SPEAKER_00] da bi tako nešto mogla realizirati.

1327
00:48:58,559 --> 00:48:59,679
[SPEAKER_00] I nisam uvjeren da bi

1328
00:48:59,679 --> 00:49:01,920
[SPEAKER_00] naišlo to na simpatije

1329
00:49:01,920 --> 00:49:04,619
[SPEAKER_00] ni nove američke vlade.

1330
00:49:04,619 --> 00:49:06,119
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, vidjeli ste sada reakcije

1331
00:49:06,119 --> 00:49:07,599
[SPEAKER_00] nakon presude

1332
00:49:07,599 --> 00:49:09,360
[SPEAKER_00] Miloradu Dodiku,

1333
00:49:09,360 --> 00:49:10,539
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, da je službeni

1334
00:49:10,539 --> 00:49:12,199
[SPEAKER_00] Washington zapravo reagirao

1335
00:49:12,199 --> 00:49:13,900
[SPEAKER_00] puno energičnije

1336
00:49:13,900 --> 00:49:14,440
[SPEAKER_00] i puno nedvosmislenije

1337
00:49:14,440 --> 00:49:16,519
[SPEAKER_00] nego što su reagirile

1338
00:49:16,519 --> 00:49:17,860
[SPEAKER_00] evropske predstavnice,

1339
00:49:17,860 --> 00:49:19,199
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, na Dodikove najave

1340
00:49:19,199 --> 00:49:22,480
[SPEAKER_00] koraka koji bi doveli

1341
00:49:22,480 --> 00:49:23,099
[SPEAKER_00] do slabljanja

1342
00:49:23,099 --> 00:49:24,599
[SPEAKER_00] unutarnje kohezije u Bojiha.

1343
00:49:24,599 --> 00:49:26,460
[SPEAKER_01] Vijest koju sam pročitao

1344
00:49:26,460 --> 00:49:27,059
[SPEAKER_01] možda jučer,

1345
00:49:27,059 --> 00:49:28,280
[SPEAKER_01] prekuće li vi ste,

1346
00:49:28,280 --> 00:49:30,539
[SPEAKER_01] tiče se rumunskih izbora

1347
00:49:30,539 --> 00:49:31,980
[SPEAKER_01] i onog proruskog kandidata

1348
00:49:31,980 --> 00:49:32,559
[SPEAKER_01] predsjednicu.

1349
00:49:32,559 --> 00:49:34,480
[SPEAKER_00] Kojemu se zabranjuje...

1350
00:49:34,480 --> 00:49:36,159
[SPEAKER_01] Sad, okej, ja znam,

1351
00:49:36,159 --> 00:49:37,159
[SPEAKER_01] suverenista ste,

1352
00:49:37,159 --> 00:49:38,659
[SPEAKER_01] ja malo naginjem tu,

1353
00:49:38,659 --> 00:49:40,320
[SPEAKER_01] ali opet je li to demokratski?

1354
00:49:40,320 --> 00:49:40,960
[SPEAKER_01] Čovjeku se zapravo...

1355
00:49:40,960 --> 00:49:42,179
[SPEAKER_00] Naravno da je nedemokratski.

1356
00:49:42,179 --> 00:49:43,619
[SPEAKER_01] Opet će i zazvat kontraefekt.

1357
00:49:43,619 --> 00:49:44,980
[SPEAKER_01] To je potpuno jasno,

1358
00:49:44,980 --> 00:49:46,460
[SPEAKER_00] ali dakle, naravno da je nedemokratski,

1359
00:49:46,539 --> 00:49:49,480
[SPEAKER_00] jer ako on krši rumunjske zakone,

1360
00:49:49,480 --> 00:49:50,440
[SPEAKER_00] onda protiv njega treba

1361
00:49:50,440 --> 00:49:51,559
[SPEAKER_00] provjeti zakonni postupak,

1362
00:49:51,559 --> 00:49:52,820
[SPEAKER_00] treba ga zatvoriti,

1363
00:49:52,820 --> 00:49:54,599
[SPEAKER_00] ako je zato propisana kazna zatvora.

1364
00:49:54,599 --> 00:49:56,800
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim, ne možete na temelju

1365
00:49:56,800 --> 00:49:58,900
[SPEAKER_00] gole sumnje i na temelju toga

1366
00:49:58,900 --> 00:50:00,800
[SPEAKER_00] što vam ne odgovaraju stajališta

1367
00:50:00,800 --> 00:50:01,760
[SPEAKER_00] koja on zastupa,

1368
00:50:01,760 --> 00:50:03,860
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, isključiti ga od izbora.

1369
00:50:03,860 --> 00:50:04,840
[SPEAKER_00] I to je potpuno jasno

1370
00:50:04,840 --> 00:50:07,019
[SPEAKER_00] da oni koji povlače takve poteze,

1371
00:50:07,019 --> 00:50:08,280
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, koji ga žele isključiti

1372
00:50:08,280 --> 00:50:09,360
[SPEAKER_00] s izbora, zapravo pirlje

1373
00:50:09,360 --> 00:50:10,699
[SPEAKER_00] granu na kojoj sjede.

1374
00:50:11,119 --> 00:50:13,579
[SPEAKER_00] Jedino je pitanje jesu li toga svjesni

1375
00:50:13,579 --> 00:50:16,420
[SPEAKER_00] ili potpuno nesvjesno rade

1376
00:50:16,420 --> 00:50:17,340
[SPEAKER_00] u korist vlastite šte.

1377
00:50:17,340 --> 00:50:18,219
[SPEAKER_01] Da, je li ono tu,

1378
00:50:18,219 --> 00:50:19,780
[SPEAKER_01] ajmo reći mali ljudi obični,

1379
00:50:19,780 --> 00:50:21,380
[SPEAKER_01] mada svi smo mi ljudi isti,

1380
00:50:21,380 --> 00:50:23,280
[SPEAKER_01] s jedne strane, aha,

1381
00:50:23,280 --> 00:50:24,659
[SPEAKER_01] mogu se promeniti spol,

1382
00:50:24,659 --> 00:50:25,480
[SPEAKER_01] nema problema,

1383
00:50:25,480 --> 00:50:26,179
[SPEAKER_01] a s druge strane,

1384
00:50:26,179 --> 00:50:27,659
[SPEAKER_01] okej, čovjek šta bi kažete,

1385
00:50:27,659 --> 00:50:29,019
[SPEAKER_01] ima takve stavove kakve ima,

1386
00:50:29,539 --> 00:50:30,219
[SPEAKER_01] ne možeš se,

1387
00:50:30,219 --> 00:50:31,820
[SPEAKER_01] misli, tu je Evropa,

1388
00:50:31,820 --> 00:50:32,880
[SPEAKER_01] tu je ona,

1389
00:50:32,880 --> 00:50:34,179
[SPEAKER_01] što sam neka smijestila sebe

1390
00:50:34,179 --> 00:50:34,940
[SPEAKER_01] u Magraću klupu.

1391
00:50:34,940 --> 00:50:36,420
[SPEAKER_01] To je onaj paradoks

1392
00:50:36,420 --> 00:50:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] tako zvane liberalne demokracije

1393
00:50:38,000 --> 00:50:39,900
[SPEAKER_00] koja, kao što smo malo prije kazali,

1394
00:50:39,900 --> 00:50:41,480
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, ne dopušta slobodu

1395
00:50:41,480 --> 00:50:42,719
[SPEAKER_00] onima koji su,

1396
00:50:42,719 --> 00:50:44,420
[SPEAKER_00] koji gledaju na stvari drugačije,

1397
00:50:44,420 --> 00:50:45,239
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, dopuštama,

1398
00:50:45,239 --> 00:50:46,920
[SPEAKER_00] mislite različito,

1399
00:50:46,920 --> 00:50:48,659
[SPEAKER_00] ali mislite to u svojoj kući.

1400
00:50:48,659 --> 00:50:49,440
[SPEAKER_00] Dok nekome odgovara, da, da, da.

1401
00:50:49,440 --> 00:50:50,679
[SPEAKER_00] E, mislite to u svome stanu,

1402
00:50:50,679 --> 00:50:51,719
[SPEAKER_00] ali nemojte mi izlezniti van.

1403
00:50:51,719 --> 00:50:52,280
[SPEAKER_01] Da, eto.

1404
00:50:52,599 --> 00:50:53,500
[SPEAKER_01] Znam da vam se žulim,

1405
00:50:53,500 --> 00:50:55,199
[SPEAKER_01] jer još posla nećemo otkrivat kakvoga.

1406
00:50:55,199 --> 00:50:57,820
[SPEAKER_01] Za kraj, očite,

1407
00:50:57,820 --> 00:50:58,900
[SPEAKER_01] mislite još da je opet

1408
00:50:58,900 --> 00:51:00,199
[SPEAKER_01] biti bojkotirani medijima?

1409
00:51:00,199 --> 00:51:02,079
[SPEAKER_01] Misli, sad ste već vi ispisni tu.

1410
00:51:02,079 --> 00:51:03,599
[SPEAKER_00] Ja mislim da blokada

1411
00:51:03,599 --> 00:51:05,059
[SPEAKER_00] onakvog tipa kao što i

1412
00:51:05,059 --> 00:51:06,860
[SPEAKER_00] onakvog intenziteta kao što je bila

1413
00:51:06,860 --> 00:51:08,019
[SPEAKER_00] prošle esene,

1414
00:51:08,019 --> 00:51:08,960
[SPEAKER_00] da više nije moguća.

1415
00:51:08,960 --> 00:51:10,139
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, sad je, sad,

1416
00:51:10,139 --> 00:51:13,960
[SPEAKER_00] ipak će mi neke stvari biti

1417
00:51:13,960 --> 00:51:15,300
[SPEAKER_00] i neki mediji će biti dostupniji

1418
00:51:15,300 --> 00:51:16,300
[SPEAKER_00] nego što su bili do sad.

1419
00:51:16,300 --> 00:51:17,199
[SPEAKER_00] S druge strane,

1420
00:51:17,199 --> 00:51:19,539
[SPEAKER_00] onima koji su kreirali

1421
00:51:19,539 --> 00:51:20,659
[SPEAKER_00] takvu predložbu

1422
00:51:20,659 --> 00:51:22,460
[SPEAKER_00] i koji su kreirali tu blokadu,

1423
00:51:22,460 --> 00:51:24,760
[SPEAKER_00] sigurno među njima ima i pametnih ljudi

1424
00:51:24,760 --> 00:51:26,159
[SPEAKER_00] koji su slatili da se to ne isplati.

1425
00:51:26,159 --> 00:51:28,300
[SPEAKER_00] Zapravo da je ta medijska blokada

1426
00:51:28,300 --> 00:51:30,179
[SPEAKER_00] meni u jednom dijelu i pomogla.

1427
00:51:30,179 --> 00:51:32,380
[SPEAKER_00] Kao što s jedne strane mi je odmogla,

1428
00:51:32,380 --> 00:51:33,639
[SPEAKER_00] ali je s druge strane i pomogla.

1429
00:51:33,639 --> 00:51:34,559
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, jer je ona bila,

1430
00:51:34,559 --> 00:51:36,900
[SPEAKER_00] što sam tisuću puta ponovio,

1431
00:51:36,900 --> 00:51:38,139
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, ona je bila potvrda

1432
00:51:38,139 --> 00:51:39,059
[SPEAKER_00] i svjedočba

1433
00:51:39,059 --> 00:51:40,820
[SPEAKER_00] da nisam ničiji plaćenik,

1434
00:51:40,820 --> 00:51:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] da nisam ničiji pouzdanik,

1435
00:51:42,000 --> 00:51:42,920
[SPEAKER_00] da nisam ničiji agent,

1436
00:51:42,920 --> 00:51:43,820
[SPEAKER_00] jer da jesam,

1437
00:51:43,820 --> 00:51:45,639
[SPEAKER_00] onda bi me se pozivalo

1438
00:51:45,639 --> 00:51:47,239
[SPEAKER_00] i u večernji i jutarnji

1439
00:51:47,239 --> 00:51:48,699
[SPEAKER_00] i pozivalo bi se na HTV

1440
00:51:48,699 --> 00:51:50,039
[SPEAKER_00] i koje kakve druge televizije.

1441
00:51:50,039 --> 00:51:51,880
[SPEAKER_01] Znate kakve meni to je smiješno bila?

1442
00:51:51,880 --> 00:51:52,280
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim,

1443
00:51:52,280 --> 00:51:54,219
[SPEAKER_01] aj, relativno se znamo,

1444
00:51:54,219 --> 00:51:56,860
[SPEAKER_01] ali danas stvarno ne možeš nikom

1445
00:51:56,860 --> 00:51:58,420
[SPEAKER_01] ukrasti prostor,

1446
00:51:58,420 --> 00:51:59,559
[SPEAKER_01] svijedokste,

1447
00:51:59,559 --> 00:52:01,099
[SPEAKER_01] mobitel, dva mikrofona,

1448
00:52:01,099 --> 00:52:02,739
[SPEAKER_01] platforme mreže.

1449
00:52:02,739 --> 00:52:04,320
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, nekoga i...

1450
00:52:04,320 --> 00:52:05,179
[SPEAKER_01] To je apsolutno,

1451
00:52:05,179 --> 00:52:06,119
[SPEAKER_01] kontra, kontra je,

1452
00:52:06,119 --> 00:52:07,500
[SPEAKER_01] to je meni toliko smiješno

1453
00:52:07,500 --> 00:52:08,840
[SPEAKER_01] da sam mora ovo reći.

1454
00:52:08,840 --> 00:52:09,619
[SPEAKER_00] Jasno, ali dakle,

1455
00:52:09,619 --> 00:52:12,300
[SPEAKER_00] prije 35 ili 40 godina je bilo to ono

1456
00:52:12,300 --> 00:52:13,559
[SPEAKER_00] na razini,

1457
00:52:13,559 --> 00:52:14,559
[SPEAKER_00] ali bilo je na razini

1458
00:52:14,559 --> 00:52:15,519
[SPEAKER_00] zaustavite Reuters.

1459
00:52:15,519 --> 00:52:16,780
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, to je ono

1460
00:52:16,780 --> 00:52:17,739
[SPEAKER_00] u komunizmu bilo

1461
00:52:17,739 --> 00:52:18,559
[SPEAKER_00] zaustavite Reuters,

1462
00:52:18,559 --> 00:52:20,079
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, spriječite objavljivanje,

1463
00:52:20,079 --> 00:52:20,820
[SPEAKER_00] vijesti, ne znam,

1464
00:52:20,820 --> 00:52:22,480
[SPEAKER_00] da se ruši berlinski zid.

1465
00:52:22,480 --> 00:52:23,719
[SPEAKER_01] Može, mogu tomu

1466
00:52:23,719 --> 00:52:24,940
[SPEAKER_01] i oni će ugasiti ovdje,

1467
00:52:24,940 --> 00:52:26,260
[SPEAKER_01] ali neko će drugive tvoriti,

1468
00:52:26,260 --> 00:52:27,159
[SPEAKER_01] tako da...

1469
00:52:27,159 --> 00:52:29,900
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, želim vam puno sreće,

1470
00:52:30,340 --> 00:52:30,840
[SPEAKER_01] spriha.

1471
00:52:30,840 --> 00:52:33,360
[SPEAKER_01] Krenite s poslom,

1472
00:52:33,360 --> 00:52:34,840
[SPEAKER_01] a mi možemo na kavu.

1473
00:52:34,840 --> 00:52:35,679
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala vam lijep.

1474
00:52:35,679 --> 00:52:36,500
[SPEAKER_01] Ljudi, hvala.

1475
00:52:36,500 --> 00:52:37,579
[SPEAKER_01] Vidimo se, čujemo se.

1476
00:53:00,340 --> 00:53:07,159
[UNKNOWN] Hvala vam.

